# 📊 Power BI Dashboard Projects

This repository contains a collection of **interactive Power BI dashboards** developed to analyze business, sales, finance, and entertainment data.  
These projects showcase strong skills in **data modeling, DAX, visualization, and business storytelling**.

---

## 🚀 Dashboards Overview

---

## 1️⃣ AW Sales Dashboard

**Description:**  
A complete sales performance dashboard built to analyze revenue, orders, returns, and product performance across regions and time.

**Key Features:**
- Date range slicer for dynamic analysis
- Monthly revenue, orders, and returns KPIs
- Category & subcategory-wise sales distribution
- Top products by orders and profits
- Region-wise analysis (Europe, North America, Pacific)
- Interactive map visualization

**Skills Used:**
- DAX measures & KPIs  
- Time intelligence  
- Drill-through & navigation  
- Business-focused visual design  

---

## 2️⃣ Corporate Spend Analysis Dashboard

**Description:**  
A financial analytics dashboard focused on **YTD IT spend analysis**, comparing actual vs planned spending and identifying variances.

**Key Features:**
- Actual vs Plan spend by IT Area
- Variance % analysis by country/region (map)
- Period-wise spend trends
- Sankey visual for variance flow
- Dark theme corporate UI

**Skills Used:**
- Advanced DAX calculations  
- Financial variance analysis  
- Custom themes & UI design  
- Executive-level reporting  

---

## 3️⃣ Netflix Content Analysis Dashboard

**Description:**  
An entertainment analytics dashboard providing insights into Netflix movies and TV shows across countries, genres, and years.

**Key Features:**
- Total titles, movies, shows & IMDB score KPIs
- Country-wise content distribution
- Genre-wise and age certification analysis
- Release year trend analysis
- Movie / Show toggle navigation
- Interactive slicers

**Skills Used:**
- Data cleaning & transformation  
- Trend and categorical analysis  
- Interactive navigation & UX  
- Data storytelling  

---

## 4️⃣ Choco Boom Sales Dashboard

**Description:**  
A product-focused sales dashboard created for a chocolate brand (**Choco Boom**) to track sales performance across products, months, years, and regions.

**Key Features:**
- Year selector (2023 / 2024)
- Month-wise slicer
- KPIs: Total Sales, Avg Sales, Total Orders, Avg Cost per Box
- Product-wise sales ranking
- Category comparison (Bars, Bites, Other)
- Region-wise sales (APAC, Americas, Europe)
- Sales trend over time
- Page navigation buttons (Main Page, Sales Person, Delish, Juicies, Tempo, Yummies)

**Skills Used:**
- Power BI data modeling  
- KPI & DAX calculations  
- Time-based analysis  
- UX-focused dashboard design  

